graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMesh -->|metadata storage| etcd[etcd v3.5.4+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|model artifacts| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|CRD definitions| KServeCRDs[KServe CRDs v0.11.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics CRDs| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics collection| Monitoring[ODH/RHOAI Monitoring<br/>INTERNAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|routing, mTLS| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>INTERNAL OPTIONAL]

    %% Integration Points (components that consume ModelMesh)
    Dashboard -->|model deployment| ModelMesh
    Monitoring -->|scrapes metrics| ModelMesh

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|runtime images| ModelServers[Model Servers<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]
    ModelMesh -->|adapter image| RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>v0.11.1]
    ModelMesh -->|framework image| ModelMeshRuntime[ModelMesh Runtime<br/>v0.11.1]
    ModelMesh -.->|REST translation| RestProxy[REST Proxy<br/>v0.11.1 OPTIONAL]

    %% Styling
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External required
    style etcd fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServeCRDs fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External optional
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Runtime components
    style ModelServers fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RuntimeAdapter fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMeshRuntime fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RestProxy fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
